sentences: By 1996 she settled in London where she occasionally performs at Wigmore Hall and plays Valentine Silvestrov's piano works for the British premiere.
She had a huge success with in Kharkov State Philharmonic in Eastern Europe and following that became professor of its conservatory.

Currently she works as a director of the Tsukanov Scholarship Fund and is a teacher at the Royal College of Music, many students of whom were Wieniawsky, RCMJD, and Martin Musical Competition winners.
